data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home where comfort and style blend seamlessly on an oversized corner lot. The main level features beautiful laminate flooring. The inviting living room beckons with a slider that opens to the backyard's deck, creating a perfect flow for indoor-outdoor living. The kitchen boasts an abundance storage and prep space. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area, with its own slider to the yard, is a delightful space for enjoying meals with a view. The main level also hosts a cozy family room complete with a fireplace, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Perfect for gatherings or quiet evenings by the fire. As you go upstairs, you will discover three well-appointed bedrooms. The primary bedroom impresses with double closets and an attached bathroom, providing a private retreat within the home. Step outside to the spacious fenced backyard, offering the perfect backdrop for entertaining + RV Parking. Easy access to Mt Hood, downtown Troutdale, Sandy River and more!
